This is a 16 vs 16 player Awp Map

This map was made similar to my most recent release (Awp_Sewer) im enjoying making aim style maps but with a bit more detail than normal, although the detail is slightly higher the FPS is still all there as it is highly optimized. 

The map is 100% symmetrical so no team advantage, Hope you enjoy!

Please leave feedback!

Thanks,
